$WmMPID_フローラ,ch05_41_Flora_F_Normal,Face|I am Flora. For my master, and to
fulfill the terms of my contract, I will
eliminate you.$k$p$Sbs1000|

$WmMPID_ヘルビンディ,ch00_12_Helbindi_M_Normal,Face_Anger|Hey, brat! You and your friend better
hurry up if you don't want to die!$k$pYou can bet the guards've noticed
by now. Don't be surprised if they
catch up!$k$p$WmMPID_ユルグ,ch00_15_Yurg_F_Normal,Face_Pain|Augh! These ruins...they're so
confusing!$k$p$WmMEID_ヴェロニカ,ch00_04_Veronica_F_Normal,Face_Pain|It's like a maze in here. But perhaps
that's why we have yet to be caught.$k$p$WmMPID_ユルグ,ch00_15_Yurg_F_Normal,Face_Pain|Up...and down... Up...and down... I'm
so tired!$k$p$Sbs2000|$WmMPID_ヘルビンディ,ch00_12_Helbindi_M_Normal,Face_Anger|If you got time to whine, you got time
to run!$k$p$EFace_Cool|Now, you two...you go on ahead. I'll
catch up.$k$p$SbpBGM_EVENT_SERIOUS_01,0|$WmMPID_ユルグ,ch00_15_Yurg_F_Normal,Face|Wait, what? But what about—$k$p$WmMPID_ヘルビンディ,ch00_12_Helbindi_M_Normal,Face_Anger|Get going! Or I'll smack you with my
axe!$k$p$WmMPID_ユルグ,ch00_15_Yurg_F_Normal,Face|O-OK.$k$p$WmMPID_ヘルビンディ,ch00_12_Helbindi_M_Normal,Face|Why can't she just do what she's
told?$k$pAll right. Here we go...$k$p$WmMPID_スルト,ch00_07_Surtr_M_Normal,Face|I thought I heard a mouse...but
instead I find the animal I had
protecting the border.$k$pI remember you, treasonous cur.$k$p$WmMPID_ヘルビンディ,ch00_12_Helbindi_M_Normal,Face_Pain|King—$k$p$WmMPID_スルト,ch00_07_Surtr_M_Normal,Face_Anger|Save your excuses. It's far too late.$k$pYou would rebel against me? Foolish,
helpless, and weak... It is time for you
to die.$k$p$EFace_Smile|You are trash, plucked from the
gutter. In Múspell, we burn trash. As
your sister learned to her regret...$k$p$WmMPID_ヘルビンディ,ch00_12_Helbindi_M_Normal,Face_Pain|Rrgh!$k$p$WmMPID_スルト,ch00_07_Surtr_M_Normal,Face_Smile|Do you have something to say? Last
words? Speak!$k$p$WmMPID_ヘルビンディ,ch00_12_Helbindi_M_Normal,Face|Something to say? Yeah, I think I do.
What you got coming to you...you
deserve it.$k$p$WmMPID_スルト,ch00_07_Surtr_M_Normal,Face_Anger|You dog!$k$p$WmMPID_ヘルビンディ,ch00_12_Helbindi_M_Normal,Face_Anger|Keep running, brat. Keep running...$k$p$Sbs150|
